<subSubSection pageId="4" pageNumber="439" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1436,1368,1897]" pageId="4" pageNumber="439">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,297,1368,1393]" pageId="4" pageNumber="439">Description.</emphasis>
Vertex yellowish brown with some black stripes. Eyes brown. Pronotum with irregular yellowishbrown stripes (
<figureCitation box="[320,389,1404,1429]" captionStart="FIGURES 1–12" captionStartId="2.[151,264,1939,1961]" captionTargetBox="[154,1432,275,1903]" captionTargetId="figure@2.[151,1436,267,1915]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURES 1–12 Longicornus flavipuncatus Li &amp; Song: 1. ♂, dorsal view; 2. ♂, lateral view; 3. ♂,face; Longicornus longus Xing &amp; Li: 4. ♂, dorsal view; 5. ♂, lateral view; 6. ♂,face; Longicornus furcatus sp. nov.: 7. ♂, dorsal view; 8. ♂, lateral view; 9. ♂,face: Longicornus biprocessus sp. nov.: 10. ♂, dorsal view; 11. ♂, lateral view; 12. ♂,face." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1441737/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="439">Fig. 7</figureCitation>
). Face with frontoclypeus broadly yellowish brown dorsally, without dark transverse streaks on both sides (
<figureCitation box="[314,382,1440,1465]" captionStart="FIGURES 1–12" captionStartId="2.[151,264,1939,1961]" captionTargetBox="[154,1432,275,1903]" captionTargetId="figure@2.[151,1436,267,1915]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURES 1–12 Longicornus flavipuncatus Li &amp; Song: 1. ♂, dorsal view; 2. ♂, lateral view; 3. ♂,face; Longicornus longus Xing &amp; Li: 4. ♂, dorsal view; 5. ♂, lateral view; 6. ♂,face; Longicornus furcatus sp. nov.: 7. ♂, dorsal view; 8. ♂, lateral view; 9. ♂,face: Longicornus biprocessus sp. nov.: 10. ♂, dorsal view; 11. ♂, lateral view; 12. ♂,face." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1441737/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="439">Fig. 9</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1436,1368,1897]" box="[199,677,1476,1501]" pageId="4" pageNumber="439">External features as in generic description.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1436,1368,1897]" pageId="4" pageNumber="439">
<emphasis box="[199,373,1512,1536]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="439">Male genitalia.</emphasis>
Male pygofer side broadly rounded in lateral aspect, with 7 long postero-ventral setae (
<figureCitation captionStart="FIGURES 27–33" captionStartId="5.[151,264,1225,1247]" captionTargetBox="[165,1421,209,1194]" captionTargetId="figure@5.[151,1436,195,1203]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURES 27–33. Longicornus furcatus sp. nov. 27. Male pygofer side, lateral view; 28. Valve, ventral view; 29. Subgenital plate, ventral view; 30. Aedeagus, ventral view; 31. Aedeagus, lateral view; 32. Connective, dorsal view; 33. Style, dorsal view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1441743/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="439">Fig. 27</figureCitation>
). Aedeagal shaft short and robust, with pair of furcate processes arising from ventral margin near base; gonopore apical (
<figureCitation box="[346,482,1584,1609]" captionStart="FIGURES 27–33" captionStartId="5.[151,264,1225,1247]" captionTargetBox="[165,1421,209,1194]" captionTargetId="figure@5.[151,1436,195,1203]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURES 27–33. Longicornus furcatus sp. nov. 27. Male pygofer side, lateral view; 28. Valve, ventral view; 29. Subgenital plate, ventral view; 30. Aedeagus, ventral view; 31. Aedeagus, lateral view; 32. Connective, dorsal view; 33. Style, dorsal view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1441743/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="439">Figs. 30, 31</figureCitation>
). Connective with arms nearly 1/3 length of stem (
<figureCitation box="[1050,1128,1584,1609]" captionStart="FIGURES 27–33" captionStartId="5.[151,264,1225,1247]" captionTargetBox="[165,1421,209,1194]" captionTargetId="figure@5.[151,1436,195,1203]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURES 27–33. Longicornus furcatus sp. nov. 27. Male pygofer side, lateral view; 28. Valve, ventral view; 29. Subgenital plate, ventral view; 30. Aedeagus, ventral view; 31. Aedeagus, lateral view; 32. Connective, dorsal view; 33. Style, dorsal view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1441743/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="439">Fig 32</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
